		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Big Four auditors</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The <b>Big Four</b> are the four largest international <a href="/wiki/Accountancy" title="Accountancy">accountancy</a> and <a href="/wiki/Professional_services" title="Professional services">professional services</a> firms, which handle the vast majority of <a href="/wiki/Financial_audit" title="Financial audit">audits</a> for <a href="/wiki/Public_company" title="Public company">publicly traded companies</a> as well as many <a href="/wiki/Private_company" title="Private company" class="mw-redirect">private companies</a>. The Big Four firms are shown below, with their latest publicly available data:</p>
<table class="wikitable">
<tr>
<th>Firm</th>
<th>Revenues</th>
<th>Employees</th>
<th>Fiscal Year</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/PricewaterhouseCoopers" title="PricewaterhouseCoopers">PricewaterhouseCoopers</a> <a href="http://www.pwc.com/extweb/ncpressrelease.nsf/docid/31479FE5AF3412CF852574D4005641AA" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.pwc.com/extweb/ncpressrelease.nsf/docid/31479FE5AF3412CF852574D4005641AA" rel="nofollow">[1]</a></td>
<td>$28.2bn</td>
<td>155,693</td>
<td>2008</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><a href="/wiki/Deloitte_Touche_Tohmatsu" title="Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu">Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu</a> <a href="http://www.deloitte.com/dtt/section_node/0,1042,sid%253D147431,00.html" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.deloitte.com/dtt/section_node/0,1042,sid%253D147431,00.html" rel="nofollow">[2]</a></td>
